				<strong class="adsimple-121761454"> Value:</strong> 8912691894970695056,0,0,0,0<br />
				<strong class="adsimple-121761454"> Purpose: </strong>This cookie is saved under the domain track.adform.net. It stands for the client ID and is used to offer you improved advertisements. It can forward more relevant adverts to the user and helps to improve reports on campaign performance.<br />
				<strong class="adsimple-121761454"> Expiry date:</strong> after 2 months</p>
			<p>
