				<strong class="adsimple-121761454"> Value:</strong> zOtj4TWxwbFDjaATZ2TzNaQmxrU121761454-1<br />
				<strong class="adsimple-121761454"> Purpose:</strong> The cookie is stored under the domain doubleclick.net. It serves the purpose of registering your actions following an impression or a click on the ad. Thus, it can be measured how our visitors like an ad.<br />
				<strong class="adsimple-121761454">Expiry data:</strong> after 1 month</p>
			<p>
